Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过离我们还有一段距离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上他了吗 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这味道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是佐助出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是和在下用一样的洗发水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种绿野般的清香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.82,0:02:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对错不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 还是我的毛发比较有光泽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种关键时刻不要说这些无聊事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的味道跟小狗一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟小狗一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟小狗一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你们别冲在在下的前面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影的过错 面具下的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别想再继续逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在我爱罗这样的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭遇这个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况相当不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勘九郎 带我爱罗先走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子交给我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 手鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙可不是你一个人能对付的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们砂之国的重要任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先考虑我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 这家伙是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 勘九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们逃不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是宇智波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的查克拉也所剩无几了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他使用写轮眼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况就会更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都得让他耗费大量查克拉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一鼓作气用千鸟解决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算保留查克拉对付我爱罗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法.镰鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法.风砂尘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想办法解决那把麻烦的扇子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这样能撑到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于认真起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.凤仙花之术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接命中她的要害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.豪火球之术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法.镰鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 竟然是替身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没多余的时间陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗 无论如何都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个年轻人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事发突然无法理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊 大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练成那个禁忌之术了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离开木叶的十几年 吃了不少苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个可怕的异类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以没有选择你当第四代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为那种扭曲的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于被你们发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明设下了很多陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我很惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到您会亲自出马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近村里从下忍到中忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至连暗部的上忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都陆续下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也收到你最近形迹可疑的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像您这样的忍者 怎么会做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看连你也一起杀掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸 这一切果然是你干的好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说 你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么隐瞒也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在开发忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然为了这种事拿同伴做实验
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是禁忌之术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要学会所有的忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解这个世界所有的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个把蓝色和黄色混合在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将调出来的颜色称为绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在也只是在做相同的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色是查克拉 黄色是印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后绿色是忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与无限种色彩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世上的忍术应该也有千百万种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:11:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为了学会所有的忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到真理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须投入漫长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有投入漫长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底了解一切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才有资格被称为究极个体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉体的寿命实在太短暂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过无常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是火影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要死亡 一切都灰飞烟灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你躲在这里实验的忍术是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 你猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是长生不老之术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这长生不老之术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是让自己的灵魂永世留存的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 先找到新的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让自己的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占据那具肉体的转生术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以扮成以前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想让老师怀念一下过去的种种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衰老真是好空虚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的感受更加深刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将会死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我则会获得更年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更强悍的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶带给我好多乐趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 是宇智波佐助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 被你说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取他人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让自己的灵魂永存的转生术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张脸和身躯是第几个了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是第二个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备把佐助培养成我喜欢的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再夺取他的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让您对自己的一生后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并诅咒着命运而死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这张脸比较合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么能大意呢 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您每次都这么天真
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不像你的作风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗藏着恶意与野心的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我早就察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此 但我却假装不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个战乱的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才华横溢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个十年难得一见的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我希望你能继承我的衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我天真的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造就了如今的现状
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您打算现在杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法.通灵之术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿飞老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他 猿飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿飞 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我不忍杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我要杀了你弥补当年的过错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么用影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以让所剩无几的查克拉继续分散呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然老了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过于焦虑 想缩短自己的寿命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巳 亥 未 卯 戌 子 酉 午 巳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个印…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿飞果然要用那招吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是第四代火影说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有与这个术\N订下契约的人才能看到的死神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你做什么都太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶就此灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓火影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为保护这个家而屹立不倒的栋梁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是继承了木叶意志的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不会轻易倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻术.暗行之术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只不过是木叶这个组织的历史中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个暂时的领袖而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算留有石像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一天也会被风化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶对我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是单纯的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶每年都会诞生许多忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为保护村子而活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为保护重要的人而战斗并牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算村里的同伴没有任何血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都是我最重要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就打断你这根栋梁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让木叶这个家垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根栋梁也不会断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是继承了第一代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和第二代火影意志的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第三代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你用什么方法觊觎木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承我意志的新任火影将会成为栋梁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续保护木叶这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 第四代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就施展你从未见过的秘传忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印术.尸鬼封尽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶每年都会诞生许多忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为保护村子而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为保护最重要的人而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便彼此没有血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们仍是我最重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会让你继续伤害我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁术奥义 尸鬼封尽
